long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Wharf is an in-browser assistant designed to automate repetitive recruiting and GTM tasks. Imagine a scenario where you need to navigate through a list of links and perform a specific action, such as reviewing a candidate profile to find specific attributes. Wharf is the tool that can streamline this process for you!

Watch a demonstration of Wharf in action, automating prospect targeting on LinkedIn, here: https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7150591700715945985/.

For more information, visit: https://dotshq.notion.site/Wharf-8749e8106c6a4aa9b3557497a694214d
